{"word":"H1097 - בְּלִי - bᵉlîy - bel-ee' - Corruption","slug":"H1097","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">בְּלִי</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>bᵉlîy"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>bel-ee'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Corruption"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D1;&#x05BC;&#x05DC;&#x05D9; - b<sup>e</sup>l&#x0131;&#x0302;y</b> - <i>bel-ee'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H1086\">H1086</a>; properly <i>failure</i>, that is, <i>nothing</i> or <i>destruction</i>; usually (with preposition) <i>without</i>, <i>not yet</i>, <i>because not</i>, <i>as long as</i>, etc.: - corruption, ig[norantly], for lack of, where no . . . is, so that no, none, not, un[awares], without."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1077\">H1077</a>, <a href=\"#/H1086\">H1086</a>, <a href=\"#/H1087\">H1087</a>, <a href=\"#/H1094\">H1094</a>, <a href=\"#/H1099\">H1099</a>, <a href=\"#/H1100\">H1100</a>, <a href=\"#/H1107\">H1107</a>, <a href=\"#/H1115\">H1115</a>, <a href=\"#/H8399\">H8399</a>"}]}